    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "yhLBExcsRwix4GJBJ9WPbLf9LJML/JW4r/sJtgaqAqk=",
    "originContent": "You can *[cook](https://ratatui.rs/)* a terminal. But can you **deep fry** a terminal?",
    "translatedContent": "You can *[cook](https://ratatui.rs/)* a terminal. But can you **deep fry** a terminal?  "
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "bQVWesJ/+dHxfz/g0f9oq9rokl18oXvw5jhw6Mc1pu8=",
    "originContent": "*YES!* You can **cook *and* fry** your `tty`! ~~Run before it's too late!~~",
    "translatedContent": "*YES!* You can **cook *and* fry** your `tty`! ~~Run before it's too late!~~"
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "MwkPX9odL3XKWrt6ToZ8CmFB1XjxwCxlt9tpHjT1bAE=",
    "originContent": "> The terminal is usually in \"cooked\" mode, or canonical mode.",
    "translatedContent": "> The terminal is usually in \"cooked\" mode, or canonical mode.  "
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "zxWa117Y7ugf+Sn5GN0r4nSd2/9PSKYheaiIxYTUkw4=",
    "originContent": "> With `ratatui`🐁, it's in raw mode, but it \"cooks\" for you.",
    "translatedContent": "> With `ratatui`🐁, it's in raw mode, but it \"cooks\" for you."
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "X1LB8VwpH/40hMKtvoPh8g381g0XYYF2Oi3NW3jAD/k=",
    "originContent": "Markdown can obviously be rendered pretty well in terminals, but one key aspect is missing: ",
    "translatedContent": "Markdown can obviously be rendered pretty well in terminals, but one key aspect is missing:   "
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "eJeDn3XSE/6QOA1eBFpj7tRBYt3admnj+NooLcL67ho=",
    "originContent": "Big Headers™ make text more readable, and rendering images inline is very convenient.",
    "translatedContent": "Big Headers™ make text more readable, and rendering images inline is very convenient."
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "Ldy4IZ0hjDIq93mBPg/qGYRnytzJrIwpApkkJiaZhpY=",
    "originContent": "# How?",
    "translatedContent": "# How?"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "QbeYBJJlHCWNzn7JwJ05fXkboz+a9vIMVb0izULCMK8=",
    "originContent": "By rendering the headers as [images with ratatui](https://github.com/benjajaja/ratatui-image),",
    "translatedContent": "By rendering the headers as [images with ratatui](https://github.com/benjajaja/ratatui-image),  "
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "6D60xRxkHtmOuZPfGKZxd/WENeBEWgFVcDfWlEVW3Is=",
    "originContent": "and using one of several terminal graphics protocols: Sixels, Kitty, or iTerm2.",
    "translatedContent": "and using one of several terminal graphics protocols: Sixels, Kitty, or iTerm2.  "
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "MZjUhQXVfxpCW8VSNlYisgIBy7uCCay+qsIDCZMbpko=",
    "originContent": "The Kitty terminal also implements a [Text Sizing Protocol](https://sw.kovidgoyal.net/kitty/text-sizing-protocol/)",
    "translatedContent": "The Kitty terminal also implements a [Text Sizing Protocol](https://sw.kovidgoyal.net/kitty/text-sizing-protocol/)  "
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "AqDay38ub+8mokjTiNIsEULRfKSaDhvDpCtnhJQpgrc=",
    "originContent": "to directly scale text without needing to render as images!",
    "translatedContent": "to directly scale text without needing to render as images!"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
