    "originContent": "  * If chafa is not available at all, or you don't care about it because your terminal supports some graphic protocol, then use `--no-default-features`.",
    "translatedContent": "  * If chafa is not available at all, or you don't care about it because your terminal supports some graphic protocol, then use `--no-default-features`."
  },
